{"date":"1999-09-22","platform":"全部游戏","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a6/55/4145_4vPzo.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a6/55/4145_4vPzo.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a6/55/4145_4vPzo.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a6/55/4145_4vPzo.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a6/55/4145_4vPzo.jpg"},"summary":"本作的前半部份发生于《生化危机2》之前，女主角吉儿(Jill Valentine)于生化危机的洋馆事件后，一直调查有关Umbrella公司的地下业务。当时美国联邦政府决定以核弹彻底毁灭拉昆市，Jill Valentine于是展开她的逃亡之旅。在逃亡期间，她受到Umbrella公司欧洲分部派来Raccoon City的生物武器追迹者（Nemesis）追杀，并且遇上了隶属于Umbrella Biohazard Countermeasure Service（UBCS）的男主角卡洛斯(Carlos Oliveira)，以及UBCS成员Mikhail Victor、Nicholai Ginovaef。Jill Valentine及Carlos Oliveira逃至市政府时，Jill Valentine不幸受到追迹者攻击而感染了T-病毒，于是Carlos Oliveira便到Umbrella公司旗下的附属医院寻找解药。\r\n\r\n本作的后半部份发生于《生化危机2》之后，Jill Valentine已经康复过来，于是继续出发逃命。此时美国联邦政府已经准备发射导弹实施“灭菌作战计划”，Jill Valentine需要在15分钟内离开拉昆市。最后，在垃圾处理场成功击倒追迹者，并且与Carlos Oliveira乘坐直升机离开（直升机机师相信是生化危机中的Barry Burton）。\r\n\r\nsource: wikipedia","name":"バイオハザードスリー ラストエスケープ","name_cn":"生化危机3 最后的逃亡","tags":[{"name":"Capcom","count":52},{"name":"生化危机3","count":39},{"name":"生化危机","count":34},{"name":"PS","count":25},{"name":"PC","count":23},{"name":"Jill","count":17},{"name":"AVG","count":13},{"name":"Bio3","count":13},{"name":"吉儿V5荡漾","count":8},{"name":"ACT","count":8},{"name":"我的最爱","count":7},{"name":"开门","count":6},{"name":"超时空储物箱","count":6},{"name":"打僵尸","count":4},{"name":"多平台","count":4},{"name":"1999","count":2},{"name":"BIOHAZARD","count":2},{"name":"AAVG","count":2},{"name":"云通关","count":2},{"name":"ADV","count":2},{"name":"饿~","count":2},{"name":"追踪者","count":1},{"name":"PlayStation","count":1},{"name":"日系","count":1},{"name":"经典","count":1},{"name":"视频","count":1},{"name":"恐怖冒险","count":1},{"name":"36-40","count":1},{"name":"解谜","count":1},{"name":"僵尸","count":1}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"生化危机3 最后的逃亡"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"生化危机3 复仇女神"},{"v":"バイオハザード3 LAST ESCAPE"},{"v":"Resident Evi